This Project on Restaurant Management is a general software developed (using Python) to simplify Restaurant operations by automating them.
In this project, “Chillox” is the project’s Restaurant name. It covers major aspects of Restaurant management, 
it could perform the following operations- Take a token number, Provide you Menu card, Billing and Payment.

Functions Created
Home()- Function to display the project’s main screen i.e. the home page of the project or you can say the main menu for selecting the desired operation to perform.
Token_no()- Function for creating a token number inRestaurant by entering user/customer Name and Phone Number.
Menu_Card()- Function for provides user/customer with the restaurant’s menu card to order food.
Payment()- Function for payment of restaurant bill generation.
